AudioData.Text: Welcome! I will guide you through this simulation
Now move the trolley
Push the mechanism inside
Push the mechanism and movingpart back
Close the forge
Go to terminal and push the green button to start baking
The bar is ready. Open the door
Now move the trolley
Push the mechanism inside
Push mechanism and trolley back
Put bar on the table
Take a bar  and go to slicing table
While holding the tool, you can use it by pressing the trigger button.
Now you need to cut this bar in two pieces. First, pick up the tool on the slicing table
Great. Release the tool and it will go back to its original position.
Тow take a piece of the bar and transfer it to the microscope
Pick up pice of bar and put it on microscope
Well done! Now slice the bar by moving the blade in the highlighted area.
Look through the microscope
Go to forge and open the door
Wait 10 seconds while the bar is being burned
